Feature: 
- Allows the User to search for abilities and espers by related criteria (searching for products by related)
Condition:
- Multiple button with icons displayed to allow filtering and sorting to fulfill the criteria of the search
User Story:
- As a User, I should be able to sort products by name, price, type, rating, etc.
- As a User, I should be able to filter products displayed to show only what I want or prefer

Feature:
- The shopping cart should be accessible through the whole lifetime of the app
Condition:
- Every screen the User is on should display a shopping cart on the top right corner
User Story:
- As a User, I should be able to access the shopping cart whenever I want to
- As a User, I should be able to see if the the shopping cart is empty or already has items

Feature:
- Clicking an item/ability should display a new dialog/activity and display the item/ability in full detail
Condition:
- Items/abilities is clickable and should open a dialog/activity with the extra details for said item
User Story:
- As a User, I should be able to tap on an item/ability and a new dialog/activity is shown
- As a User, I should be able to see extra details on the item/ability in the new dialog/activity

Feature:
- Users should be able to edit items/abilities in the shopping cart
Condition:
- User decides he doesn't want an item anymore, he can delete the item
- User decides he wants to get more of a certain item/ability he has in his cart, he can add items
- User decides he has too much of a certain item/ability he has in his cart, he can reduce said content
User Story:
- As a User, I should be able to remove items from the shopping cart
- As a User, I should be able modify the quantity of items I want to buy (add/remove)

Feature:
- Users can check out items/abilities in the shopping cart
Condition:
- At the shopping cart screen, User can check out and pay for their order
- (OPTIONAL) If the User has no items in the shopping cart it should display a shopping cart with 0
User Story:
- As a User, I should be able to check out and pay for the items/abilities from the shopping cart
- As a User, I should be able to tell whether or not I have items in the shopping cart
